[I] The Fraunhofer MPEG-H decoder

[T] The Fraunhofer MPEG-H decoder (mpeghdec) is a C/C++ implementation of the
[T] MPEG-H Audio standard as defined in ISO/IEC 23008-3:2022.

[U] https://github.com/Fraunhofer-IIS/mpeghdec

